headline: Tesla earnings, fresh Fed commentary: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come tomorrow, Wednesday, October 22, including corporate earnings results from companies like Tesla (TSLA), AT&T (T), and IBM (IBM), as well as economic commentary from Federal Reserve governor Michael Barr.
